          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/976.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>mayonnaise </strong>to a large mixing bowl with the <strong>horseradish cream</strong>, the <span class=\"text-highlight\"><strong>juice</strong></span> of 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span> <strong>lemon</strong>, and a generous pinch of<strong> salt</strong>,<strong> pepper</strong> and <strong>sugar</strong></p>\n<p>Add a generous drizzle of<strong> olive oil </strong>and mix to combine – this is your <strong>lemony</strong> <strong>horseradish</strong> <strong>dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
