          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Trim, then finely slice the <strong>spring onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p>\n<p>Chop the<strong> chives </strong>finely</p>\n<p>Dice the <strong>apple<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> </strong>(skin on) </p>\n<p>Add the <strong>sliced spring onion, chopped chives</strong> and <strong>diced apple </strong>to the bowl of <strong>horseradish</strong><strong><strong> </strong>dressing</strong> and set aside </p>",
